commit.message: Deprecation Warning: The 'warn' method is deprecated, use 'warning' instead

Use environment marker in install_requires

Instead of adding a requirement on `futures` conditionally, always
add it as a conditional requirement.

This is the recommended way, and enables installation with the
Poetry tool.

Also give setuptools.setup a list instead of a tuple for the
`classifiers` argument, since later versions complain about tuples.
